metadata.name: Schmrypto Banner
metadata.description:
Collector Reward - Custom Banner

All the lettering on the banner is pulled from photographs from my archive. I had to go hunt down a few specifically and was even able to include a light painting at the end. I will not re-use any of the lettering included in any of my banners for future rewards.

Thank you so much for your kind words and support.

You Rock!
